OL,3,CTwo men jailed following drugs bust on
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound cannabis farm
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed after police
OL,7,Funcovered a multi-million pound
OL,8,Fcannabis farm in Bradford.
OL,10,FOfficers from Bradford City
OL,11,FNeighbourhood Policing team attended a
OL,12,Fbuilding on Nelson Street on 25
OL,13,FNovember 2024 after intelligence
OL,14,Fsuggested there was a strong smell of
OL,15,Fcannabis coming from the building.
OL,17,FOfficers forced entry and uncovered
OL,18,Fnearly 7,000 plants in 19 rooms.
OL,20,FThe drugs are thought to have had a
OL,21,Fstreet value of #6.2 million pounds.
