OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1783521459
OL,3,CTwo men jailed following drugs bust on
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound cannabis farm
OL,6,FSheraz Ahmed, aged 24, and 65-year-old
OL,7,FHung Nguyen - both of no fixed address
OL,8,F- admitted to producing Class B drugs.
OL,10,FAt Bradford Crown Court on Tuesday 30
OL,11,FJune, Ahmed was sentenced to 27
OL,12,Fmonths, and Nguyen was sentenced to 24
OL,13,Fmonths.
OL,15,FSergeant Barry Coleman of Bradford
OL,16,FCity NPT team said: "This was a
OL,17,Fsignificant and organised operation
OL,18,Finto the production of drugs right in
OL,19,Fthe city centre.
OL,26,@xD@UOU
