FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1783521459
OL,3,CTwo men jailed following drugs bust on
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound cannabis farm
OL,6,F"We welcome the sentence handed down;
OL,7,Fdrugs have no place in our society.
OL,9,F"We are committed to taking drug
OL,10,Foffending seriously and the production
OL,11,Fof illegal drugs will not be tolerated
OL,12,Fin our communities.
OL,14,F"I would encourage anyone with
OL,15,Finformation about drugs supply to
OL,16,Fcontact West Yorkshire Police or
OL,17,FCrimestoppers to support this
OL,18,Fcontinued disruption of those involved
OL,19,Fin the supply of drugs."
